Samples

We offer a variety of samples that show how to work with the Notecard on host MCUs, as well as complete project implementations that you can reference or clone.

Note

Have an example or sample project you'd like to see? Let us know in our forum and we'll do our best to point you in the right direction.

Host MCU Samples

We offer a set of complete samples for a variety of host microcontrollers. Each set of samples contains instructions on how to set up your hardware and how to install the example code.
